1955;;Seven Angry Men;;American;;Charles Marquis Warren;;Raymond Massey, Jeffrey Hunter, Debra Paget;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Seven_Angry_Men;;John Brown (Raymond Massey) is a controversial 19th-century abolitionist. After cutting a bloody swath through Kansas, Brown and his followers take refuge in a warehouse at Harper's Ferry, Virginia, where he meets his own personal Waterloo at the hands of federal troops.